{
  "info": {
    "name": "🌱 Kishan Sathi API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Kishan Sathi – AI Crop Disease Detection Platform\n\n**Base URL:** http://localhost:8000/api/v1\n\n**Auth:** Bearer JWT token in Authorization header\n\n**How to use:**\n1. Run 'Register' to create account\n2. Run 'Login' → copy access token\n3. Set {{access_token}} variable\n4. All other requests use Bearer {{access_token}}",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",      "value": "http://localhost:8000/api/v1" },
    { "key": "access_token",  "value": "PASTE_YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "PASTE_YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE" },
    { "key": "image_id",      "value": "" },
    { "key": "report_id",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "notif_id",      "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/register/",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"ramesh_patel\",\n  \"email\": \"ramesh@example.com\",\n  \"first_name\": \"Ramesh\",\n  \"last_name\": \"Patel\",\n  \"phone\": \"+919876543210\",\n  \"state\": \"Odisha\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass@123\",\n  \"confirm_password\": \"SecurePass@123\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Register a new user. Returns JWT tokens on success.\n\n**Expected Response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Registration successful!\",\n  \"tokens\": { \"access\": \"...\", \"refresh\": \"...\" },\n  \"user\": { \"id\": 1, \"email\": \"ramesh@example.com\" }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.access) { pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', json.access); }",
                  "if (json.refresh) { pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.refresh); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/login/",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"ramesh@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass@123\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Login with email + password. Auto-sets access_token variable.\n\n**Expected Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"access\": \"eyJ...\",\n  \"refresh\": \"eyJ...\",\n  \"user\": { \"id\": 1, \"email\": \"...\", \"total_analyses\": 0 }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout/",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/token/refresh/",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Change Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/change-password/",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"old_password\": \"SecurePass@123\",\n  \"new_password\": \"NewPass@456\",\n  \"confirm_password\": \"NewPass@456\"\n}"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "👤 Profile",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/profile/",
            "description": "Returns full user profile including nested Profile object.\n\n**Expected Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"email\": \"ramesh@example.com\",\n  \"total_analyses\": 12,\n  \"profile\": {\n    \"bio\": \"Wheat farmer from Odisha\",\n    \"experience\": \"intermediate\",\n    \"farm_size\": 12.5\n  }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/profile/",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"first_name\": \"Ramesh\",\n  \"last_name\": \"Patel\",\n  \"phone\": \"+919876543210\",\n  \"profile\": {\n    \"bio\": \"Wheat and maize farmer from Rourkela, Odisha.\",\n    \"experience\": \"intermediate\",\n    \"farm_size\": 12.5,\n    \"primary_crops\": \"Wheat, Maize, Potato\",\n    \"district\": \"Sundergarh\"\n  }\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Upload Profile Image",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/profile/image/",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "profile_image", "type": "file", "src": "/path/to/photo.jpg" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Dashboard Summary",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/dashboard/",
            "description": "Returns user stats for dashboard: total uploads, disease count, recent activity.\n\n**Expected Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"stats\": {\n    \"total_uploads\": 42,\n    \"diseases_found\": 8,\n    \"healthy_crops\": 34,\n    \"avg_confidence\": 91.4,\n    \"success_rate\": 97.6\n  },\n  \"recent_activity\": [...]\n}\n```"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "📷 Analysis",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "⚡ Upload + Analyze (One Step)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.image_id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('image_id', json.image_id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/analysis/upload-analyze/",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "image",     "type": "file",   "src": "/path/to/crop.jpg" },
                { "key": "crop_type", "type": "text",   "value": "wheat" },
                { "key": "notes",     "type": "text",   "value": "Spotted orange patches on leaves" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Recommended endpoint for frontend.** Uploads crop image AND runs AI analysis in one step.\n\n**Expected Response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Upload and analysis complete.\",\n  \"image_id\": \"uuid\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"disease_name\": \"Wheat Leaf Rust\",\n    \"confidence_score\": 94.2,\n    \"is_healthy\": false,\n    \"severity\": \"high\",\n    \"chemical_treatment\": \"Propiconazole 25% EC...\",\n    \"alternative_predictions\": [...]\n  }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Upload Image Only",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.upload && json.upload.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('image_id', json.upload.id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/analysis/upload/",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "image",     "type": "file", "src": "/path/to/crop.jpg" },
                { "key": "crop_type", "type": "text", "value": "tomato" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Run Analysis on Uploaded Image",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/analysis/analyze/{{image_id}}/",
            "description": "Runs AI on a previously uploaded image. Use image_id from the upload step."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Analysis History",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/analysis/history/?page=1&ordering=-uploaded_at",
              "query": [
                { "key": "page",      "value": "1" },
                { "key": "ordering",  "value": "-uploaded_at" },
                { "key": "crop_type", "value": "wheat",  "disabled": true },
                { "key": "is_healthy","value": "false",  "disabled": true },
                { "key": "search",    "value": "rust",   "disabled": true },
                { "key": "uploaded_after",  "value": "2024-01-01", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "uploaded_before", "value": "2024-12-31", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "min_confidence",  "value": "80",         "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Single Analysis Detail",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/analysis/history/{{image_id}}/"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Analysis Record",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/analysis/history/{{image_id}}/"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Analytics",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/analysis/analytics/?period=30",
              "query": [{ "key": "period", "value": "30" }]
            },
            "description": "Returns daily chart data, top diseases, totals for the given period.\n\n**Expected Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"period\": 30,\n  \"total_uploads\": 42,\n  \"diseases_found\": 8,\n  \"healthy_crops\": 34,\n  \"avg_confidence\": 91.4,\n  \"daily_data\": [{\"date\": \"2024-03-01\", \"count\": 3}, ...],\n  \"top_diseases\": [{\"disease_name\": \"Wheat Leaf Rust\", \"count\": 5}, ...]\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Disease Library",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/analysis/diseases/?search=rust",
              "query": [{ "key": "search", "value": "rust" }]
            },
            "description": "Public endpoint. No auth required. Lists all known diseases."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "📄 Reports",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Generate Single PDF Report",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.report_id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('report_id', json.report_id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/reports/generate/{{image_id}}/",
            "description": "Generates a professional PDF report for a specific analysis.\n\n**Expected Response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"PDF report generated successfully.\",\n  \"report_id\": \"uuid\",\n  \"pdf_url\": \"http://localhost:8000/media/reports/.../crop_analysis_xxx.pdf\"\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Generate Summary Report",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/reports/generate-summary/?period=30",
              "query": [{ "key": "period", "value": "30" }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Download PDF",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/reports/download/{{report_id}}/",
            "description": "Returns the PDF as a binary download (Content-Disposition: attachment)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List My Reports",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/reports/"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔔 Notifications",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Notifications",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/notifications/",
            "description": "Returns paginated notifications with unread_count at top level."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Unread Count",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/notifications/unread-count/"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Mark All Read",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/notifications/mark-all-read/"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Mark One Read",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/notifications/{{notif_id}}/read/"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Notification",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/notifications/{{notif_id}}/delete/"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
